<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وسع رَبنَا}</span> أَيْ: مَلَأَ رَبُّنَا <span class="c3">{كُلَّ شيءٍ علما}</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{رَبَّنَا افْتَحْ بَيْنَنَا وَبَيْنَ قَوْمِنَا}</span> أَيْ: احْكُمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَإِذَا دَعَا النَّبِيُّ رَبَّهُ أَنْ يَحْكُمَ بَيْنَهُ وَبَيْنَ قَوْمِهِ، جَاءَهُمُ الْعَذَابُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>